<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>if the textarea element has the same name as its parent subform.
$form-&gt;getValues() returns a truncated value, remaining just one
character in the foo element.</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$foo = new Zend_Form_SubForm('foo') ;
$foo-&gt;addElement('textarea','foo') ;
$form-&gt;addSubform($foo,'foo') ;
</code></pre>

    </div>
</div>

